    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you... but sometimes i wonder if it would be more loving to just... not be here? to let them breathe again? i think about how much easier their lives would be if they didn't have to worry about my appointments or my pain or how i'm doing every single day. wouldn't it be a kind thing, in a way, to just stop being a burden?",
